In MSTest v4, `Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>` returns the typed value directly instead of using an `out` parameter. Here's the fix:

```csharp
// Before (v3)
Assert.IsInstanceOfType<FastProcessor>(processor, out var typed);

// After (v4)
var typed = Assert.IsInstanceOfType<FastProcessor>(processor);
```

Let me apply this to all three call sites:

